Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[Bakuman Episode 25 Translation Kewl0210]



Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.00,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,The serialization meeting starts at 2 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.13,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,It's starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.65,0:00:45.65,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Now then, I thought we'd begin the December serialization meeting for the weekly Shounen Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:49.94,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,I, Yahagi, will be the facilitator for this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:53.02,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,We have thirteen candidates for serialization this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.02,0:00:55.15,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,You've all been given a copy of each.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.02,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,We'll start with Orihara-sensei's "Tanktop."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:00.79,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,Uchida, from my group, is this work's editor. {qc shorten a little if you think it needs it}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:05.79,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,The protagonist has transferred to a prestigious private metropolitan high school, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:09.63,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}The serialization meeting's facilitator is placed in a position above the captains.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:15.63,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}Firstly, the captain of the work's editor explains the aim of the story and its current situation.{\i0} {qc not sure if I've interpreted what kewl means here correctly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:20.77,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}The presented names have already been looked over one week beforehand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:22.72,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}The editor's impressions are written on the exterior of the envelopes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:26.69,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}The attendees hold the meeting after reading those impressions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:29.69,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,As everyone's assessments state, I think he should be cautious here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:33.32,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Okay then, would everyone please share their thoughts on this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:36.44,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Well, after his last work was a hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:40.69,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,If you take the reader's expectations into account, it's a little weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:44.56,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,But he's changing his literary style. I don't think it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:49.54,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,It's not bad, but the Orihara-san style of boldness seems faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:52.04,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It most certainly seems like he's feeling his way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.81,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,It's a no. Have him rework it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.17,0:02:08.31,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}The works presented in the meeting are divided into groups of "yes" and "no" for serialization.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:10.57,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}Works given a "no" can be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:13.05,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}designated to be reworked and looked at again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:14.92,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}tested out as one-shots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.36,Main,Narration,0,0,0,,{\i1}or simply rejected and discarded.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.55,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Works that are given a "yes"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.00,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,become new series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:24.33,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,To make room for them, editors also decide which series will be ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:27.90,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,These last questionnaire results haven't been too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:28.98,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:30.31,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:33.89,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,Ever since the time when five were selected at once, they've only chosen three at most. {qc if you think it needs it, I reworded this like 5 times and I just cba lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.62,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You sure are carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.75,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,Really? If you think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.53,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apart from the already popular authors,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.54,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,{\i1}lately they're being more critical than ever,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:43.80,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,{\i1}even towards serialization-level mangas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:57.80,Main,Eiji,0,0,0,,Happy crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:00.58,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,I guess they're already underway by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.16,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.68,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Yuujirou-san told me earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:08.00,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,that there are thirteen candidates for serialization at this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.74,0:03:13.28,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,And that usually at most two new series get serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.75,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Maybe there will be more today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:18.60,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Plus, four authors in it have previous experience being serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:22.30,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Even if a newcomer gets through, it's not gonna be more than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:24.55,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,O–One?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:26.97,Main,Eiji,0,0,0,,First sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.50,Up of Main,Eiji,0,0,0,,Let me explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:31.95,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Whoever gets serialized, let's not hold any grudges, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.02,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,O–Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.52,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Next is "hideout door."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:38.09,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,I'm the editor in charge of this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:42.18,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,After the results from the Golden Future Cup, I had them write serialization names.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.86,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,The original story author, Aoki, is a third year university student, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:48.33,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,she had three one-shots published in shoujo magazines over a relatively short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:51.75,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,She can also produce original stories in the name form very efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:55.35,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,I'm sure many of you know about the artist Nakai,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:59.09,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,who's been an assistant to various senseis over the past 12 years. {perhaps revise the use of sensei here as it's not being used as an honorific}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.09,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,You could call him a veteran who has been supporting Jack from behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.51,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,I have nothing to criticize about his artistry or skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:11.18,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Personally, I'd like to give him his place in the spotlight. {qc original - 'give him his place in the sun', spotlight suits better in English imo, whatever you think}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.35,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Both of them have quite a lot of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:19.63,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Even after serialization, I think they're the types that would last a long time without losing momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:30.46,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to think that shounen manga was the right way to go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.91,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was runner-up for the Story King...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:37.79,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in the Golden Future Cup, although I felt good about it, the result was...{\i0} {qc original = 'But in the Golden Future Cup, while I felt a good response, the result is...' I might have misinterpreted}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.96,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's because it's shounen manga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.13,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I'm sure it'll be okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:50.30,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,Nakai-san's drawings certainly bring out the view of Aoki-san's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:54.10,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Even though they didn't win the Golden Future Cup, they did receive good results.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:05:00.01,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,Yes, but there were three works that got good results in the Golden Future Cup and they're all in this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.24,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,We have to balance them with the other works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.52,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,There's no fantasy story like this in Jack right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.70,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,I think maybe we should hold onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.51,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,It'll be fine to give it a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.20,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:11.72,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.37,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,"Ki wo Kikasete Kirakira."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.37,TL Notes,TL Note,0,0,0,,Ki wo Kikasete Kirakira = Play it Smart and Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.66,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,I told you, they're not done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.82,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,But I'm so worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.65,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,I said I'd call you when I heard more, so calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.59,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.97,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.26,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,So what do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.81,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Two pair, tens and fours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:31.31,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Jacks, three of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.51,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Jack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.04,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,It's been two hours already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:41.27,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,They usually finish in about two hours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.94,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,If it goes quickly. {qc original = 'If it goes fast.' Might have changed the meaning a bit much, see what you think}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.80,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,This isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.55,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Playing cards isn't getting my mind off it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.95,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.29,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,We'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.93,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,We've done all we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:01.71,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:11.68,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Mi–Miyoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.57,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Just invite her over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:16.68,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,My heart can't take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.72,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,So it's a no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.72,0:06:20.60,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,Then let's discard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:23.30,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Next, one of the works from the Golden Future Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.79,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,"KIYOSHI Knight," Fukuda Shinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:28.62,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,It was previously done as a one-shot and ranked 7th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:33.37,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Given the improved results it got in the Golden Future Cup, I think it would make a fitting manga for Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:37.63,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,The author, Fukuda, is twenty years old, so he's near the age of the readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:41.42,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,He creates characters that are easy to relate to, which is a great strength for a series. {qc original = He creates sympathetic characters which would be a strength to have in a series.' not entirely sure if he does indeed mean sympathetic, or characters you can emphasize with}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:44.60,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Also, his editor, Yuujirou, will give him strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.94,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,He's definitely got strong characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:51.97,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,But this really seems like the type that would only be interesting as a one-shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:55.19,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Honestly, these three chapters all follow the same pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:56.46,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,The first three chapters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:58.89,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,are purposefully done similar to the popular one-shot to give readers a grip on the series. {qc, too long, hard to reword, original = The first three chapters are purposefully done with like what was popular with one-shot to give readers a grip on the series.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:02.26,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,It's important to make sure you do what is typically well received. {qc}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:03.70,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.11,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,The impression you get after reading them is too similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.44,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,It kind of feels like all it has is vigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:09.11,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Having vigor is a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:12.38,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,Well, I'm still worried about what I said before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.49,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,The one-shot and the Golden Future Cup showed results.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.85,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Above all, the characters are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:19.33,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,Let's give it a yes for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.79,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,{\i1}For now, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.79,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,Okay, next is Arai-san's "Cheese Okaki."{Said under Yoshida's line.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:22.79,TL Notes,Somebody,0,0,0,,TL Note: Okaki is a kind of rice cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:24.22,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Yoohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.74,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,I thought we should try to take our minds off things, so I brought some playing cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:28.51,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.29,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.05,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.99,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.67,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,On top of fixing what we pointed out last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:39.27,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,the increase of the group organization aspect can have value.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.46,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,It seems like something that could be a media franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:46.24,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,In terms of improvement, I'd like the characters to be a little cooler, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.03,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,It's like that because friendly character's are Arai-sensei's specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:51.21,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,We can give it a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.19,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:55.77,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,But Editor-in-Chief, of the seven we've looked at, you've given four a yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.16,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how many there are. Interesting works are given a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.23,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Next is "Rakko 11-Gou," Hiramaru Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:03.23,TL Notes,TL Note,0,0,0,,Rakko 11-Gou = Otter #11
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:05.54,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Eh, I'm the editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:07.66,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,He's my top recommended newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.84,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,Oh? You seem confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:14.38,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Top recommendation? All he's won is an honorable mention in the monthly award, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:17.11,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Hiramaru-san is 26 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.97,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,But until this year, he hardly ever read manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:24.19,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,When he was on a train, he took a copy of Jack off the luggage rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.90,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,and suddenly thought, "Even I can draw something like this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.18,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,That day, he handed in a letter of resignation to his job at a corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:31.18,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,then a month later, he submitted something to us .
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.65,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,So that's Rakko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:39.88,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Most people start liking manga when they're young and submit things trying to imitate manga they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:44.73,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Then they start to learn how to draw manga from books and things. {qc}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:48.04,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Tons of material like that is out there now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:52.73,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,But Hiramaru-san, from just one issue of Jack and by his own trial and error,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.81,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,without even knowing about screentone, submitted something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:09:00.22,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,What's more, he's creating characters that could quickly be made into an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:03.71,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,He went from a total amateur to that in just one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:04.64,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,He's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.34,0:09:08.60,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,If we go by that story, he does seem to be a good prospect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.60,0:09:10.92,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,But I don't know about serializing him so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:12.90,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,There's a high risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.81,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,It's interesting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:16.18,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,The name is good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.13,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,It's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.00,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:19.99,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.02,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Okay then, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.48,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,"Gitantei TRAP."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:25.33,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.93,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,The editor is Hattori, from my group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.17,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,It's the mystery story that even got good results in the Golden Future Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:44.52,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,I know you all must be concerned since the authors are still only in their second year of high school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:49.09,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Let me say this first, they can draw while going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:49.90,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,What's your basis for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:55.61,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,In addition to the names they've submitted to the meeting, they made seven more serialization names.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:59.90,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,They did five chapters at the pace of a nineteen page manuscript every two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:02.62,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,All while making progress on drawing for the Golden Future Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.15,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,While they were working on the Golden Future Cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:10.41,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,While honoring their deadlines, they made works that were no worse than the names being passed around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:13.29,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,They've got incredible motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.46,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Hey, want to go have fun somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.63,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Being outside would distract you from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:21.14,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Takagi will get the outcome on his cell phone anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.52,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:26.10,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,I don't want to get really happy or really upset someplace in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.10,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.25,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.42,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,What do you think your chances are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:37.61,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,If it's about getting serialized or not, it's already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.36,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it really like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.26,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.04,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,But 20% would be optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.99,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Why? You won the Golden Future Cup, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:48.88,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,The realistic result of the Golden Future Cup was that three works were at about the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.96,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Even if you consider it to be one out of three, that's 33%.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.78,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,And we can't even say for sure that they'll pick one series from the Golden Future Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.37,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Will even one get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:11:01.47,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Hattori-san always said he was worried about us still being in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.75,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,But that "CROW" guy is a high school student, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.43,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Shouldn't it be okay, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.52,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Niizuma Eiji is a precedent, so he's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:13.02,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,They don't need anyone else to sell as a genius high schooler, so we're a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:18.20,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,It's getting kind of negative in here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:19.15,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:23.29,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,If they're in their second year, then won't they graduate in just a year from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.10,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,Why does it have to be right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:28.65,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,It's certainly pretty harsh to try to compare them to Niizuma-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.50,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.89,0:11:32.90,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,It seems that those two are well aware of Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:36.42,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,They themselves are interested in doing this while going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.17,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,If that's what they want, wouldn't it be all right to let them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:43.13,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Well, they don't need to walk down that thorny path...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.13,0:11:47.00,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,They've come into the editorial department a lot, starting from when they were in middle school, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.14,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,They're the exact opposite of Hiramaru-kun from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.77,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,Everything they've done has been for the purpose of becoming mangakas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.38,Main,Heishi,0,0,0,,What I mean is, they're not very newcomer-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:57.40,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,It's true that they've been adamantly making names ever since NEXT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.73,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Almost to a creepy degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:02.49,Main,Someone,0,0,0,,But for a mystery story, the information is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:05.96,Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Won't that quickly get really hard for young people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:11.29,Main,Someone,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't want them to have such a hard time that they turn it into a battle manga midway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.03,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,I think that having read ten chapters of names before the meeting, we can expect a lot from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.82,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,But there are concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:18.14,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,They're too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.14,0:12:21.85,Main,Somebody,0,0,0,,It's certainly true that overconfidence is a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:22.47,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,But... {For the love of God, how long are they gonna hold on this shot of a phone? Did the animators give up, too?}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.84,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,The names up to chapter 3 are interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.31,Main,Sasaki,0,0,0,,It's a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.83,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.62,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:37.05,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,That sure was a long smoke break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.61,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,I just can't calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:41.76,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,You never can calm down on these meeting days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:44.73,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Is that your data about assistants from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.32,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:47.09,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,You sure are working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:50.80,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,No. If I don't occupy myself with something, I can't keep my mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:53.15,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,But everything's already all correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.25,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,They sure are taking a while this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.90,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Sure are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.59,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,But they should be done pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:02.98,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,And that makes all thirteen reviewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:08.46,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,But there are seven yeses, and we can't serialize them all, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.06,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,I think we should try to narrow it down a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.27,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,He really did all that, eh? That Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.39,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Ten names and five manuscripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:19.42,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,I can tell how serious he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:22.03,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,You brought in a real secret as well, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.98,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,A guy quitting his business job to be a mangaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.99,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Let's serialize him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:32.08,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Hiramaru-san has no attachment to manga, so if he's no good, let's put a fast stop to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:37.17,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Anyone can read manga. But you can't draw it without talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.03,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,He has talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:43.38,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,For someone not to draw manga even though they have talent... It is a sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.93,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's a sin or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.68,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,but let's try not to look bad, since we're unsure about what these things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.31,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Eh? Still?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:55.32,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,How many hours has this thing been going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:57.52,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,You said it'd be over in three hours, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:00.30,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,I said it's {\i1}usually{\i0} done in three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.27,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Just keep it together and wait for me to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.59,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Well, doesn't that sound nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:06.49,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Anyhow, you've got tons of free time since you can't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.74,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Fukuda-kun, you're being way too rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:13.20,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,If by some faint chance you get serialized, first I'm going to make you show me some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.04,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "by some faint chance"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.56,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,That sounded funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:19.00,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,I totally have faith that I'll be serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.58,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,So you want me to teach you some Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:23.54,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Sounds great. You teach Japanese, I'll teach manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:26.16,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Anyway, so there's really still nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.88,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Yeah. So just wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:33.10,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Geez. I'm getting irritated about this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.41,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Want to play cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:37.06,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.06,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.69,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Definitely today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:45.65,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,That call sure is taking a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.72,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,I wonder if that means we didn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:50.86,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,It'd probably be hard for him to tell us the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.78,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,They won't want to fuss over newcomers like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.79,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,If we don't get it, of course he'd tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.90,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Man, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.39,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,H–How about some dinner? I could make some.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.38,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,I couldn't swallow anything at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:05.70,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,You don't have to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:07.88,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.25,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I want to... get serialized...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:15.47,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was being tested with the one-shot and the Golden Future Cup...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.35,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time, I'm definitely...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.65,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serialization...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.22,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,{\i1}With Aoki-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:25.65,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.76,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Who's the idiot who suggested this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.76,0:15:31.35,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,Wasn't that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.32,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Let's quit this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:35.21,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,But man, this is running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.34,Main,Kimu,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:39.69,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Well, the longer it is, the more of a chance we have, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:40.88,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:45.48,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,If a lot of new works are starting, that means a lot of old ones are also ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.21,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:50.01,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Waiting it out sure isn't easy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.28,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Aida group, this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:53.26,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Ah, he got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:55.16,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Yoshida, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.22,Main,Yahagi,0,0,0,,Then we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:15:59.89,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.60,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,It–It's Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:04.81,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.37,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,He said... congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.61,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,WE DID IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:24.45,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,SERIALIZATION!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.57,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:24.45,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.33,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Let go of me, Miyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.33,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,It's Yuujirou.{KmE: Check this line's timing i'm not sure}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.33,Up of Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Unfortunately you didn't get serialized. {These two are said under the other few lines}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:28.02,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,I lost again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:30.55,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,But you were in the last seven series.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:30.55,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.89,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,There are four new series.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:35.11,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,It was really a close fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.93,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:40.60,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Every one of them was interesting, but they said they'd like to see a manga mainly upheld by story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:44.78,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,That's why I told you I should've drawn it as more of a continuing story!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.73,Main,Yuujirou,0,0,0,,Is that so? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.36,Main,Nakano,0,0,0,,We did it. "Cheese Okaki" is serialized!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:52.31,Main,Yoshida,0,0,0,,Congratulations. Just as I thought, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:56.06,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,In the next serialization meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:59.82,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,At our next meeting, I'll give you the details and information for—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:03.99,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you give me some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:04.95,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:06.82,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.79,Main,Aida,0,0,0,,I'll call you again another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:10.20,Main,Aoki,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:14.71,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Yes. Then we'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.69,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.94,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:19.01,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,This isn't a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:21.49,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Yeah. Stop that, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.23,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,My face won't stop grinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.22,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Saikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.81,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Thanks. This is because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.49,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Shuujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:32.63,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I should say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.85,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Without you, Shuujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.50,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to continuing to work with you, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:41.07,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.83,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,That's so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.05,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Friendship between two boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.30,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Ah, Mashiro, you need to tell Miho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:48.95,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:52.64,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to Miho's instant response!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.27,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,Serialization...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:17:58.92,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:03.44,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Why don't you talk with Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:05.22,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,Eh? I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.52,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Yes you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.23,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,You should at least give him a proper and direct "Congratulations!" for an occasion like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.49,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.81,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,No, it's from Fukuda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:21.15,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's he calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.89,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-kun, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.28,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,I lost to you again! It's frustrating as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.27,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.66,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Both me and Nakai-san got overlooked this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:33.98,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,But listen good! At the next serialization meeting, I'm definitely getting through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:36.84,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,So don't get canceled or anything before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.59,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you guys to make a popular manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.96,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.74,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.55,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,I'm handing you over to Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.52,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Ashirogi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.06,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:52.01,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Just as I promised, I've waited and continued to be serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.37,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm delighted that we'll be able to work hard while competing with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:55.11,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I'm not losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.94,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It'll be all {\i1}zugyuun{\i0}. {That's not a word, nor is it supposed to be.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:58.05,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.05,0:19:00.48,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I think it's because of you that we were able to get serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.64,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,We'll be looking forward to competing against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.44,Main,Eiji,0,0,0,,I am as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.80,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Man, oh man. Fellow serialized authors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:09.10,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.20,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rivals?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.62,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:12.64,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,Fukuda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:14.73,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,We'll definitely get serialization next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.64,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Of course, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:19.10,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,No way in hell I'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.10,0:19:23.63,Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,And you've gotta work hard, or Aoki-san's gonna dump you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.99,Main,Nakai,0,0,0,,We're not even going out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.72,Up of Main,Fukuda,0,0,0,,Ah, I knew that's what you were going for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:33.14,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,So even though they didn't get it, both Fukuda-san and Nakai-san were laughing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:37.22,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Yeah. With those two, you can bet they'll get it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.38,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,You haven't gotten a reply from Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:41.11,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,It doesn't always come right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.25,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Maybe she's at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:43.35,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.08,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Well, you'll get a reply later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.39,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Okay, let's celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.67,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Should I go buy a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.69,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Maybe some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.97,0:19:51.32,Main,Kaya,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.55,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Serialization?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.75,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Yeah. Starting February of next year in Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.37,Main,Grandpa,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:02.70,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Serialization, but what about school? {There's a reason why these characters never show up in the manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.01,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I'll do it while going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.77,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,While going? It's not that simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.96,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I'm definitely going to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:10.14,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.16,Main,Grandpa,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.59,Main,Grandpa,0,0,0,,Moritaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.09,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.26,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.97,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:24.78,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I finally got serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.65,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I've been trying to be a mangaka for two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.99,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I'm still a gambler, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.89,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.65,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Why're you acting so distant about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:59.35,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,You, Dad, and Moritaka are all being naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.11,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,That's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.65,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,This is the result of his hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:04.56,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,We should be sincerely happy for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:05.56,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Men have—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:07.70,Up of Main,Mom,0,0,0,,Men have dreams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:08.98,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:11.95,Main,Mom,0,0,0,,You know, once in a while, even women can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:16.84,Main,Dad,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:23.45,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uncle said...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:24.59,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}if you kept after your dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.22,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of Shuujin, I could take the first step.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:40.54,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... no matter how hard it is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:43.09,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you kept going and never gave up, what you'd achieve would be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.60,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of Azuki...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:06.14,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}I–I'm going to be drawing the art, and he's doing the stories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.35,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.35,0:22:09.95,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow! Then I'm sure you'll make it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:13.30,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}S–So if our manga gets turned into an anime,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:15.41,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}then we'll reserve the role of heroine for you or something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:16.39,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:17.41,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so happy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:19.06,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll work hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:22.67,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll become a seiyuu and appear in your anime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:24.10,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}How great!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:30.91,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}So if that dream comes true, please marry me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:44.21,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,A number I don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:46.42,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,Mashiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:48.63,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,It's Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:49.88,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:52.80,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,I got your number from Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:56.77,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for hanging up on you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:59.68,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, too, for not really saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:00.73,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:03.15,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.26,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,On serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:07.07,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:09.79,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,We got another step closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:11.77,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,To our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:13.01,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:15.99,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,And to make that dream come true, I'm going to work even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:18.92,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.33,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,I can even talk on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:23.79,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:25.09,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:29.73,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,If talking to you makes me this happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.08,0:23:32.60,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.43,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,that someday our dream will come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:37.90,Main,Azuki,0,0,0,,and a time will come when we can always be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:40.52,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.20,0:23:44.36,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Okay, preparations are all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.59,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Let's have Hattori-san sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.59,0:23:48.65,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Try not to be too nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:53.36,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,We've got lots of stuff to talk about, like contracts and assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.07,Main,Both,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:58.31,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Congratulations on serialization.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.31,0:24:00.12,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Th–Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:02.94,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are there two people?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:04.33,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he here for the contracts or something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.38,Main,Miura,0,0,0,,I'm Miura, I joined Jack last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:08.57,Main,Miura,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:10.15,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.15,0:24:10.94,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:13.89,Main,Hattori,0,0,0,,Your editor will be Miura from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:15.47,Main,Both,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:17.39,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,H–Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.26,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,It's ending here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:19.83,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,Awesome! I'm so hyped for the continuation!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.39,Main,Saikou,0,0,0,,Will we really be all right with Miura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:23.38,Main,Shuujin,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to our series?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.38,0:24:27.12,Main,Ashirogi,0,0,0,,For the continuation of the dream, look forward to season two!
