Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:47.54,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought to myself, "Why is it so hard for me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:52.75,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,as I saw everyone around me looking happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:01:00.39,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I talked with you, I felt just a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:05.93,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because we spoke our minds about the same sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:13.57,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,But at times when we couldn't each others faces,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:20.66,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,the feeling of our spirits being crushed overwhelmed us like a monster, but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:26.95,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,we could say from our hearts that we were happy to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:29.75,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of people increases little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:33.34,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,and as we reflect upon that warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:39.59,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,supporting each other and dealing with our abjection together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:42.55,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,we're now definitely on our way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:46.45,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll be able to walk forward now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:52.94,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,After we count on our fingers all the things we lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:02:02.66,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,with the hope we have now, we try to count up the light we're going to obtain from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:10.16,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,We could say from our hearts that we were happy to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:12.95,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of people increases little by little
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.14,0:02:16.57,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,and as we reflect upon that warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:22.58,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,supporting each other and dealing with our abjection together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:25.75,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,we're now definitely on our way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:33.18,ETL,,0000,0000,0000,,to the place we can't reach alone.
