Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:11.94,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I look up at a spring sky, full of nothing but worries
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:16.20,English,,0000,0000,0000,,and hang my head
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.83,English,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm looking up again
