Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.71,0:21:33.63,English,,0000,0000,0000,,In this town you were determined to find
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:37.85,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that shouldn't be lost and keep them in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:46.35,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I would find them in this town
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:55.36,English,,0000,0000,0000,,and hold to my chest the things I must not lose
