Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:06.75,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see that bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:14.05,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness is always, feeling invisible colors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:36.65,English,,0000,0000,0000,,I muttered "Love" alone to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:40.87,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories, like petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:46.16,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Carried on a gentle wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:49.17,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:55.67,English,,0000,0000,0000,,A blue bird flying through a blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.92,0:23:00.01,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see that bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.09,0:23:07.31,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness is always, feeling invisible colors
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:13.02,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Your love flies across my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:17.19,English,,0000,0000,0000,,That bird must have been you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:22.32,English,,0000,0000,0000,,In a sad wind, you still spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.32,0:23:26.41,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Melting into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.41,0:23:28.87,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe away the tears, dry your wings
